parameters: Hmm... it won't open from this side.
If we make a lot of noise,
Maybe we can get them to open up.
What a pitiful way to make a ruckus.
Even though they've calmed down a lot already,
they started to act up again...
C'mon, I'm here to get you out of here.
You catch us then release us again...
I wasn't the one that captured you.
Well, my friends of the same race can
be a bit extreme, but there's a bit of a problem...
Well, it is a base for Cow monsters.
But, why would we be imprisoned in
Well, none of your business, though.
To see behind the Mana Ranch?
But first, allow me to thank you.
It's due to my smarts, though!
I feel like we're in no position for this...
If it's okay with you, may I

I'm going to check on the child trapped
in the back to the west.

Right, we lost to a monster...
I thought we'd be back in Ainoa, though.
We probably didn't end up dying.
I mean, I'm aching all over here.
...Yes, we should've recovered once we revived.
The fact that we didn't means that
Our possessions weren't taken away, so
we can just use the Wing Stone to return.
Damn, these monsters are weak sauce.
Then perhaps we can take advantage of this situation.
Maybe there's something interesting around here.
